{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671590/extras/wormhole_logo_outline_white.png?t=1734120483\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671590/extras/wormhole_planet_destroy.gif?t=1734120483\" /> <strong>BECOME EXTINCTION INCARNATE </strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671590/extras/wormhole_planet_destroy.gif?t=1734120483\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> In <strong>WORMHOLE</strong>, you're a giant space worm eating, shooting, dashing, and exploding your way through the cosmos. This adrenaline-fuelled arcade action game features galaxies to consume, a stackable perk system, worms with cowboy hats, and a spooky chiptune soundtrack ripped straight from Dracula\u2019s tape deck. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671590/extras/wormhole_planet_destroy.gif?t=1734120483\" /><strong> EAT EVERYTHING <i>(except yourself) </i></strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671590/extras/wormhole_planet_destroy.gif?t=1734120483\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A worm of cosmic proportions takes a lot of energy to sustain itself. Turn galaxies into your personal buffet by devouring every planet and critter in your way! Enemies have more to offer than just an energy source, so find the right moment to strike and take full advantage of the effects eating each foe can unleash.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy the multitude of benefits travelling through spacetime has to offer! Warp through wormholes to navigate obstacles, refill your energy, and quickly find your next meal.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671590/extras/wormhole_planet_destroy.gif?t=1734120483\" /> <strong>FEATURES </strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671590/extras/wormhole_planet_destroy.gif?t=1734120483\" /></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chomp your way through 100+ handcrafted levels in the main mode, and see how long you can survive your favourite stages in marathon mode!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become extinction incarnate with three abilities (DASH, CLAW, and YEEHAW), each offering a unique flavour of destruction.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Maximize your destructive potential using a variety of stackable perks designed to create cosmic chaos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wriggle your way to the top of the leaderboard against your friends and players worldwide!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the dark, vast expanses of space in a black and white style inspired by early arcade games. If spooky minimalism's not your speed, choose from over 60 delicious unlockable colour palettes to flavour the galaxy any way you like.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy 40+ original tracks, ranging from spooky space goth to high energy gabber bangers.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"COLLECTOR","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2671590/10f9317ac6fa10551596ebf562f87ceebb8f0054.jpg"},{"name":"GRABOID","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2671590/3c65ab0f02b1c04e6846926fbc4123a889db7803.jpg"},{"name":"EXOGORTH","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2671590/cd10c7d4fc71f2fee5e106d5fe4537a911aec7ec.jpg"},{"name":"SHAI-HULUD","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2671590/00b9b5c0fefa063267bb6855af684590baa8cbf8.jpg"},{"name"